org.beiter.michael.eaudit4j.processors.jdbc.propsbuilder

Class MapBasedJdbcPropsBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beiter.michael.eaudit4j.processors.jdbc.propsbuilder.MapBasedJdbcPropsBuilder

  • public final class MapBasedJdbcPropsBuilder
extends Object
    This class builds a set of JdbcProperties using the settings obtained from a Map.

    Use the keys from the various KEY_* fields to properly populate the Map before calling this class' methods.
